HEADWORD: Latchet
<hw>Latch"et</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>lachet</ets>, from an OF. dialect form of F. <ets>lacet</ets>
plaited string, lace dim. of <ets>lacs</ets>. See <er>Lace</er>.]</ety>
<def>The string that fastens a shoe; a shoestring.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

